title: Stories of Week 5/22: Uvalde Shooting, Uvalde Timeline, Primary Results, Housing Market, & More!
description:
Krystal and Saagar cover the Uvalde shooting news, timeline leading up to the Uvalde slaughter, Georgia GOP primaries, Dem battle in Texas, housing market, Elon accusation & Hillary's Russiagate lies!
